		"description": "<p>At 6th level, you gain resistance to radiant damage.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you may call upon your celestial blood to briefly take on some of their traits. As a bonus action, you cause a pair of spectral, angelic wings to appear on your back, granting you a fly speed equal to your Speed. These wings last a number of rounds equal to your Constitution modifier. If you are still airborne when this effect ends, you are incapacitated, or you drop to 0 hit points, you fall at a rate of 30 feet per round. Once you have used this ability, you may not do so again until you complete a long rest.</p>",
